extendedInfo.description: Visit El Paso: The official iPhone App for the El Paso Convention & Visitors Bureau as developed by Phidev Inc.This is your complete guide for a memorable visit to the El Paso Southwest. You will find up-to-date and accurate information about El Paso's culture, attractions and hotels plus local stores and restaurants. Itineraries with stop-by-stop directions offer great half- and full-day excursions.Integrated maps show your location and the location of your planned destination.Personalize your experience using the Favorites function. When on any listing, tap the heart icon to save to your Favorites. Our Near Me function will locate nearby restaurants, stores, attractions and hotels.El Paso: Real adventure is still alive.
